{"tid":1811260,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"估唔到死左2500幾人, 比想像中大10倍","createTime":"2020-01-04T13:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T15:38:08.000Z","uid":60200,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0481999e9b42584548717fc5de0300b5151ce046","tid":1811260,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"唔好問我來源, 純粹感慨"},{"pid":"0988d4dfcefab473aa361f92ac439878bfdc4868","tid":1811260,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"你咁講好難信你wor<br />\n<br />\n不過我知你實答我唔信就唔好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64f02ebfa3fbf14d85ac67f76d613004c99c6a6","tid":1811260,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解2003年沙士香港有299人死亡？而新加坡得33人？差唔多十倍呀仆你個街！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為當年個仆街政府草菅人命，冇一早隔離大陸病人！<br />\n<br />\n咁你信唔信依家呢個政府會話俾你知真相？佢咁驚經濟差，仲會提你帶口罩？佢就係唔想人人帶口罩！<br />\n<br />\n你諗吓，假設你喺大陸中咗招，知道喺大陸好大機會死，而死咗官方都唔會認，咁你又知道香港醫生好犀利，咁你會點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾我就會先搭車去深圳，再落嚟香港，咁你個海關唔通每個大陸人都檢疫咩？仲係靠人自願申報？你都戇鳩鳩嘅！<br />\n<br />\n同埋，你真係信大陸淨係武漢出事？唔會由武漢spread去其他省份？<br />\n<br />\n為求自保，出街帶口罩啦<br />\n<br />\n要一人行一步，防止社區爆發呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFrgXW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFrgXW1.png&h=6510022b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZaEUdw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZaEUdw.png&h=9c751baa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEvJBhZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEvJBhZ.png&h=95690e68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X59uwRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX59uwRt.png&h=40f9ad0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08TZUer.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08TZUer.png&h=dc5f3de9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOtZUes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOtZUes.png&h=eb37c162&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c2d26b6af0ac05fbade565e0f20daf9d70b45b6","tid":1811260,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0481999e9b42584548717fc5de0300b5151ce046","tid":1811260,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"唔好問我來源, 純粹感慨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"真係好慘烈 有D重送埋上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0fda81098dd382223227b781888091396a902c","tid":1811260,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"連家屬？"},{"pid":"f9743cdcdd0222686e9d44c03cb754f20f01a0ad","tid":1811260,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"有數字即係起碼有紀錄先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d04affcafc9bc984cb653f62092460c2ad5b007","tid":1811260,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c2d26b6af0ac05fbade565e0f20daf9d70b45b6","tid":1811260,"uid":2585